, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Roger Leigh est né en 1366, à Coton, Shropshire, Angleterre, son père, John Leigh, avait 26 ans et sa mère, Ellen Corona, avait 26 ans. Il a épousé Johanna Burnell environ 1390, à Acton Burnell, Shropshire, Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1420, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 54 ans."},"de":{"1366–1420":"1366–1420","1365–1420":"1365–1420","1378–1400":"1378–1400","1398–1450":"1398–1450","1340–1402":"1340–1402","1340–1408":"1340–1408","about 1390":"um 1390","1402":"1402","1400":"1400","1378":"1378","1366":"1366","1398":"1398","1420":"1420","1365":"1365","1340":"1340","1450":"1450","1382":"1382","1408":"1408","Acton Burnell, Shropshire, England":"Acton Burnell, Shropshire, England","Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, England, United Kingdom","Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, England","Coton Hall, Nordley, Alveley Parish, Shropshire, England":"Coton, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom","Coton, Shropshire, England":"Coton, Shropshire, England","lifeSummary":"Als Roger Leigh 1366 in Coton, Shropshire, England geboren wurde, war sein Vater John Leigh 26 und seine Mutter Ellen Corona 26. Er hat um 1390 in Acton Burnell, Shropshire, England Johanna Burnell geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb 1420 im Alter von 54 Jahren in seinem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"1366–1420":"1366–1420","1365–1420":"1365–1420","1378–1400":"1378–1400","1398–1450":"1398–1450","1340–1402":"1340–1402","1340–1408":"1340–1408","about 1390":"about 1390","1402":"1402","1400":"1400","1378":"1378","1366":"1366","1398":"1398","1420":"1420","1365":"1365","1340":"1340","1450":"1450","1382":"1382","1408":"1408","Acton Burnell, Shropshire, England":"Acton Burnell, Shropshire, England","Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, Angletè, United Kingdom","Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, England","Coton Hall, Nordley, Alveley Parish, Shropshire, England":"Coton, Shropshire, Angletè, United Kingdom","Coton, Shropshire, England":"Coton, Shropshire, England"},"hu"